myRecipe 
python 3.8.3
django 3.2.7

This application automatically decides menu for you and tells what you need to buy at grocery. 

Features (* mean ones added to the first version)
* randomly decides menu
* can choose how many meals you want this app decide 
- or which meals (e.g. only dinners, lunch and dinner)
* provides recipes 
- decides menu based on preferred genre
- decides menu based on your life style (e.g. gain weight, lose weight, vegitarian, single)
- has an option to include leftover 
* tells groceries you need to buy according to the menu

For the first version, the user choose only single life style and menu meets normal nutrition 